.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
.TP
.B TMUX_NEW_CWD
Current working directory for session
.TP
.B TMUX_NEW_SET_NAME
Override session name
.TP
.B TMUX_NEW_SOCKET_FILE
Socket name passed to tmux -L. Use "default" (the default) to skip -L and use tmux's normal socket
.TP
.B TMUX_NEW_SAVE_INTERVAL
Seconds between auto-save runs of the background loop (default: 300)
.TP
.B TMUX_NEW_RESURRECT_DIR
Directory tmux-resurrect saves to and reads from. Defaults to $TMUX_NEW_CONFIG_DIR/sessions/$TMUX_NEW_SOCKET_FILE - one snapshot dir per tmux socket. Applied to the running server via the @resurrect-dir tmux option
.TP
.B TMUX_NEW_CONFIG_DIR
Configuration directory location
.TP
.B RUN_OPTIONS_DIRS_PROJECTS
Default project directory
.TP
.B RUN_OPTIONS_DIRS_DOCKER_SRC
Docker source directory
.TP
.B RUN_OPTIONS_DIRS_GITHUB_DOCKERMGR
